{"lemma":"غُصّاتُ","slug":"غُصّاتُ","root":"غ.ص.ص","root_slug":"غ-ص-ص","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ص-ص","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"غُصَّة","root":"غصص","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n31918"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8F%D8%B5%D9%91%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"what sticks in the throat, anxiety, anguish"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ɣusˤ.sˤa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n31918","headword_ar":"غُصَّةٌ","root":"gS","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing lying across in the throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces, so as to cause a choking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an obstruction, thereof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IDrd, A, * K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing by which one has his throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces, choked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obstructed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"food by which one has his throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces, choked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obstructed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajFA","text_ar":"شَجًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) [which has another meaning that will be found below; and both these meanings may be intended by it in the S; but in the K, the latter only seems to be intended; for there, between it and the explanation which is here first given, we find intervening the pl., and also, in the CK, the words"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqado AagoSaSotuhu fAgotaS~a","text_ar":"وَقَدْ اَغْصَصْتُهُ فاغْتَصَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":";]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a thing by which one is choked"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajFA yugaS~u bihi","text_ar":"شَجًا يُغَصُّ بِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", Lth, JK, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Haroqadap","text_ar":"حَرْقَدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"head of the windpipe"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (Lth, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(JK:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guSaSN","text_ar":"غُصَصٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb, K.) It is said in the Kur [lxxiii. 13],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waTaEaAmFA *aA guS~apK","text_ar":"وَطَعَامًا ذَا غُصَّةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And food that sticks fast,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by which one is choked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Jel,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Bd, Jel.) ―         -b2-  And hence, (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Choking wrath"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b3-  [And (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Grief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disquietude of mind;"},{"kind":"text","text":"a signification often occurring; and app. intended by the explanation"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ajFA","text_ar":"شَجًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the K. See what is said on this point above.] ―         -b4-  Hence also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guSaSu Almawoti","text_ar":"غُصَصُ المَوْتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The chokings,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"strangulations, of death: the deathrattles:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the agonies of death"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","TA","JK","Bd","Jel"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}